These tiny darlings will easily become everyone's favorite in your home right from kids to elders.

name: Minsed Chicken
description: Gorgeously ground to perfection using automated systems, our minced chicken is free of trimmings, fat, bones, and sinews. name: Chicken Drumsticks
description: The lower quarter of the chicken’s leg, our mouth-watering, meaty chicken drumsticks are meticulously cut for even cooking. name: Chicken Whole Leg
description: A combination of chicken drumstick and thigh, our whole chicken leg with a higher fat content, is a wonderfully juicy cut of meat. The rich flavors of the bone percolate deep within the meat once it is cooked.Ideal for: Roast, grill or make it in a tandoor, this is one cut you can never go wrong with!Freshness Indicator:The chicken should be pink in color and cold to touch.Tips: As the legs work harder than any other part of the chicken, the meat is firmer and needs to cook longer.

name: Chicken Liver

name: Chicken Thigh and leg (Boneless)

It can also be cooked in banana leaves to make a great side for a portion of steamed rice. The scampi is popularly eaten with the head. This larger scampi is perfect for those who love prawns.

name: Baby_carp(Baby catla-Rohu)

Because of its famous health benefits, this fish is usually used in the preparation of a thin stew with vegetables to promote better health in the undernourished and the sick. It is quickly digested by the body and is a great choice for young kids as well. Properly scaled, gutted and packaged with the head and tail, baby carp can give an extra nutritional kick to any meal.
